<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_3742"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3742-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3742">Rebuilding Project Assessment by Overseas Beneficiary Neighborhoods&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/6475-4049">dbw</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">3 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">It has been said that the total dollars lost in rebuilding Iraq is greater than that lost in the Madoff Scandal.  No-bid contracts characterized the reconstruction program, money was lost without a trace. To assure that reconstruction funds do good for their intended neighborhoods, we propose a assessment and rating system in which beneficiary neighborhoods must sign off before final payment to the contractors helping rebuild their neighborhood.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_3742" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_3742', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2251&topicID=3742')">Comments (0)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_3742"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2251">Performance Appraisal</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=international overseas usaid reconstruction">international overseas usaid reconstruction</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_3742"></div>
</div></td>
