<div id="Idea_3587"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3587-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3587">Support Managers and Hold Them Accountable&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/6834-4049">Lisa Blomgren Bingham</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">4 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Managers need to be held accountable for building their own and their staff’s competencies in public engagement and collaboration. They also need access to education and training in order to learn how to build collaboration into governance at the earliest stages and with a dedicated budget. </div>
