<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_2517"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2517-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2517">US Patent & Trademark Office should link performance appraisal of managers and FOIA Officers to transparency&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/3906-4049">Patent Examiner</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The performance of USPTO managers and FOIA officers who seek to suppress information about patent operations that may shed light on corrupt managerial practices -should be judged under their performance appraisal plans as evidence of poor performance.<br/><br/>For example, for managers who order destruction of documents such as the manager who ordered the destruction of 2nd pair of eyes lists as revealed in an email released under FOIA request 07-370 (this email was dated August 15, 2006 and sent at 12:44 PM), this type of behavior for managers should be frowned upon and should be appraised negatively.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2517" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2517', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2251&topicID=2517')">Comments (2)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2517"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2251">Performance Appraisal</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2517"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr id="row_2515">
<td width="120" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
<div id="DiscussionTopicVote_2515">
<div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2515', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2251&topicID=2515&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 7</div><div>Votes Against : 14</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2515'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_2515" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 10 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 7</div><div>Votes Against : 14</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_2515'))">-7</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_2515', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2251&topicID=2515&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
