<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_2515"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2515-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2515">USPTO Should be made to post information on its performance appraisal ratings&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/3906-4049">Patent Examiner</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Everywhere I comment on this board, I'm doing so in my personal capacity.  The USPTO should be made to post for the public to see, information on the distribution of the performance appraisals that it has given to patent examiners.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2515" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2515', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2251&topicID=2515')">Comments (1)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2515"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2251">Performance Appraisal</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2515"></div>
